		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/08/05/today-in-small-business-is-entrepreneurship-in-decline/" data-title="Today in Small Business: Is Entrepreneurship in Decline?" data-description="Thirty bad reasons to start a business. Why more successful organizations are run by women and millennials. Why there&#039;s a shortage of truck drivers.">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
